[{"Id": 1010038, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Sayyid Ali bin Taaus in Mahjud Da’waah said while narrating from Abdullah bin Sannan; Abu Abdullah said: you shall be afflicted by suspicion, where you shall remain without a banner and no guided leader, and no one shall be rescued except those that recite the supplication of (Ghareeq) sunk person. I said: how is the supplication of Ghareeq? He said: say the following…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Syed Ali bin Tawoos Mahjud da’waat mein farmate hai; Abdullah bin Sannaan ne Imam Sadiq (a) se naql kiya hai; jald hi ek shubah daaman-gir hoga, us waqt koi na hoga jo tumhe raaste ki nishaan-dahi kare aur na hi koi Imam hoga jo tumhaari hidaayat kare, us zamaane mein koi najaat na paayega magar yeh ke Dua-e-Ghareeq padhe. Arz kiya; Dua-e-Ghareeq kaunsi dua hai? Farmaya; kaho…", "UrduDescription": "شیخ صدوقؒ نے عبداللہ ابن سنان سے روایت کی ہے کہ اس نے کہا: امام جعفر صادق ؑ نے فرمایا: وہ وقت قریب ہے جب تم شبہ کا شکار ہوجاؤ گے اور رہبر و پیشوا کے بغیر سرگرداں ہوجاؤ گے،اس شبہ کے دور میں کوئی شخص نجات نہ پائے گا مگر وہ شخص جو یہ دُعا پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8":